    "description": "《西里西亚上空的阴影》是一款设定在真实的中世纪欧洲，带有奇幻元素的暗黑动作冒险游戏。在真实的历史事件背景下，玩家将面临错综复杂的谜题、富有挑战性的战斗和需要技巧的潜行任务。玩家也会遭遇恶灵附身的邪教徒、魅魔、地狱凶兽，以及欧洲神话中各种为人所熟知的生物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/72ef010e98547e9692c5e8ac940d8da2.poster.avif?t=1763643450\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/72ef010e98547e9692c5e8ac940d8da2.webm?t=1763643450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/72ef010e98547e9692c5e8ac940d8da2.mp4?t=1763643450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >暗黑奇幻故事</h2>中世纪的欧洲正处于宗教动荡的时代，许多传教士都预言世界末日即将到来。1428年，胡斯派打响了西里西亚战役。表面上看，这个无君之国最大的威胁乃是这些异端者，实际上真正的危险却以一种截然不同的形式潜藏在阴影下，对于宗教纷争它们毫无兴趣。<br><br>玩家将从两位主角的视角体验整个故事。一个是暴脾气的胡斯派将军“海涅克”，他满口脏话，肆意破坏；另一个是富有教养的医院骑士团骑士“洛萨”，他在西里西亚防御工事的前线与兄弟们并肩作战。他们拥有着截然不同动机和世界观，以及装备和技能。不过他们的命运很快就会交织在一起，届时二人究竟是兵戎相见，还是暂收敌意并肩对抗更凶恶的敌人呢？这一切都由玩家来发现。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/665d30c7ad5de76db93188ac04928c61.poster.avif?t=1763643450\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/665d30c7ad5de76db93188ac04928c61.webm?t=1763643450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/665d30c7ad5de76db93188ac04928c61.mp4?t=1763643450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >错综复杂的谜题</h2>准备好迎接危险的旅程吧，你将面临的原创谜题绝对会让你绞尽脑汁。这些谜题的设计灵感源自于20世纪90年代经典的冒险游戏。你需要充分利用周围环境，寻找物品，获取线索，并破解谜题或编码信息。巧妙之处在于，有些问题可能有多种解法，甚至能另辟蹊径找到解决之道。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/da8e0036b2fd035216e84e69f7166830.poster.avif?t=1763643450\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/da8e0036b2fd035216e84e69f7166830.webm?t=1763643450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/da8e0036b2fd035216e84e69f7166830.mp4?t=1763643450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在暗处潜行</h2>有时你需要躲在暗处，悄悄从敌人身边经过，免得被人发现。掌握他们巡逻路线和习惯能帮助你更好地寻找最佳路径。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/4ddb2665b3281772272645fdcd7cf9a3.poster.avif?t=1763643450\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/4ddb2665b3281772272645fdcd7cf9a3.webm?t=1763643450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/4ddb2665b3281772272645fdcd7cf9a3.mp4?t=1763643450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有难度的战斗</h2>战斗机制不难理解，但想要充分掌握需要不断练习。请记住一点：敌众我寡是大忌！如果三个或更多敌人同时攻击你时，你会死亡！核心是利用敌人的失误，等待合适的时机，发起进攻。你不仅要面对骑士、村民和劫匪，还有各种不容小觑的超自然生物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/61d961bfaa15d6146143d286822e12eb.poster.avif?t=1763643450\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/61d961bfaa15d6146143d286822e12eb.webm?t=1763643450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1228500/extras/61d961bfaa15d6146143d286822e12eb.mp4?t=1763643450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏全程支持视觉无障碍。请通过游戏官网了解更多信息。",
